\begin{document}$$ f_{{{\text{contribution}}}} = \frac{1} {{n_{{{\text{items}}}} }}\quad n_{{{\text{actual}}}} = {\sum\limits_{i = 0}^{n_{{{\text{constraints}}}} } {f_{{{\text{contribution,i}}}} } } $$\end{document} The total number of relevant distances for a particular inter-atomic contact (ndist) is always an integer. The occurrence for a particular inter-atomic contact is calculated as: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
